ugin Popup</a></p>\n<p><strong>Question</strong>:</p>\n<p>I am trying to have a pop up only display on WooCommerce product pages, that\'s, I want a pop up to only show on pages http://www.mysite.com/product/XXXXX.<br />\n<span id=\"more-6839\"></span></p>\n<p><strong>Answer</strong>:</p>\n<p>In the popup editor, step 2, Display Rules, Page and Device Rules, change the rule to URL Matching, Wildcard Match, then enter the following text to the input box: <code>*/product/*</code>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/popup-wildcard-match.png\" class=\"wplightbox\"><img src=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/popup-wildcard-match-600x293.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"293\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-6842\" srcset=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/popup-wildcard-match-600x293.png 600w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/popup-wildcard-match-240x117.png 240w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/popup-wildcard-match-768x375.png 768w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/popup-wildcard-match-1024x500.png 1024w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/popup-wildcard-match-500x244.png 500w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/popup-wildcard-match.png 1178w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p class=\"lightboxtext\">Click to enlarge the image</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"How to open an email subscription popup form in Divi button module\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:119:\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-popup-plugin/how-to-open-an-email-subscription-popup-form-in-divi-button-module/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 19 Nov 2018 06:28:07 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"WordPress Popup Plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:36:\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/?p=6797\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:440:\"Product: WonderPlugin Popup Version 5.6 and above Tutorial: Divi Builder is a drag and drop page builder by Elegant Themes. This tutorial will show you how to open an email subscription form created with WonderPlugin Popup when clicking a Divi &#8230; <a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-popup-plugin/how-to-open-an-email-subscription-popup-form-in-divi-button-module/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;</span></a>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"WonderPlugin Support\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2834:\"<p><strong>Product</strong>:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-popup/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WonderPlugin Popup</a> Version 5.6 and above</p>\n<p><strong>Tutorial</strong>:</p>\n<p>Divi Builder is a drag and drop page builder by Elegant Themes. This tutorial will show you how to open an email subscription form created with <a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-popup/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WonderPlugin Popup</a> when clicking a Divi button.<br />\n<span id=\"more-6797\"></span></p>\n<p><strong>Step 1</strong> - Create a popup with WonderPlugin Popup</p>\n<p>In the popup editor, step 2, Display Rules, Page and Device Rules, make sure the popup is enabled on the post or page where you are going to add the Divi button.</p>\n<p>If you don\'t want the popup to show up automatically, in the Display Times tab, uncheck all options.</p>\n<p><strong>Step 2</strong> - Open the popup in Divi button module</p>\n<p>In Divi builder, add a button module. In Content tab, Link section, enter <code>#</code> to the Button URL input box.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/divi-popup-link.png\" class=\"wplightbox\"><img src=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/divi-popup-link.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"553\" height=\"612\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-6798\" srcset=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/divi-popup-link.png 553w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/divi-popup-link-163x180.png 163w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/divi-popup-link-542x600.png 542w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/divi-popup-link-271x300.png 271w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 553px) 100vw, 553px\" /></a></p>\n<p>In the Advanced tab, CSS ID and Classes section, enter the following text to the CSS Class input box:</p>\n<pre class=\"brush: plain; title: ; notranslate\">\r\nwppopup wppopup-id-1\r\n</pre>\n<p>In the text, the number 1 is the ID of the popup. Make sure to replace it with the ID of your own popup.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/divi-popup-class.png\" class=\"wplightbox\"><img src=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/divi-popup-class.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"560\" height=\"612\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-6799\" srcset=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/divi-popup-class.png 560w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/divi-popup-class-165x180.png 165w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/divi-popup-class-549x600.png 549w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/divi-popup-class-275x300.png 275w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Save the page, exit the Visual Builder and test it on the published post or page.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"How to integrate BitChute video to WordPress 3D Carousel\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:105:\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-carousel/how-to-integrate-bitchute-video-to-wordpress-3d-carousel/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 15 Nov 2018 00:08:26 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"WordPress 3D Carousel\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"WordPress 3D Carousel Plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"WordPress 3D Video Carousel\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"WordPress Carousel\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:36:\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/?p=6778\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:428:\"Product: WonderPlugin 3D Carousel Tutorial: This tutorial will guide you how to integrate BitChute videos to carousel created with WonderPlugin 3D Carousel. Step 1 - Get the embed URL of BitChute video In the BitChute video page, click the Share &#8230; <a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-carousel/how-to-integrate-bitchute-video-to-wordpress-3d-carousel/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;</span></a>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"WonderPlugin Support\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2880:\"<p><strong>Product</strong>:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-3dcarousel/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WonderPlugin 3D Carousel</a></p>\n<p><strong>Tutorial</strong>:</p>\n<p>This tutorial will guide you how to integrate BitChute videos to carousel created with WonderPlugin 3D Carousel.<br />\n<span id=\"more-6778\"></span></p>\n<p><strong>Step 1 - Get the embed URL of BitChute video</strong></p>\n<p>In the BitChute video page, click the Share button at the bottom right of the video player.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/bitchuteshare.png\" class=\"wplightbox\"><img src=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/bitchuteshare.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"345\" height=\"208\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-6779\" srcset=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/bitchuteshare.png 345w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/bitchuteshare-240x145.png 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 345px) 100vw, 345px\" /></a></p>\n<p>In the popup share dialog, copy the src value from the Embed Video HTML code. Please note, when copying the value, do not copy the quotes, we only need the URL wrapped by the quotes.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/bitchuteurl.png\" class=\"wplightbox\"><img src=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/bitchuteurl.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"596\" height=\"406\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-6780\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>Step 2 - Add BitChute video to 3D carousel</strong></p>\n<p>In WonderPlugin 3D Carousel, step 1, click the button <strong>Add Image</strong>.</p>\n<p>In the Add Image dialog, select an image as the carousel thumbnail, then make the following change:</p>\n<p>1. Uncheck the option \"Open current image in Lightbox\".</p>\n<p>2. Enter the BitChute embed URL to the input box \"Click to open web link\".</p>\n<p>3. Check the option \"Open web link in Lightbox\".</p>\n<p>4. Check the option \"Set Lightbox size\", change the following size value to 960 by 540. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/bitchutecarousel.png\" class=\"wplightbox\"><img src=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/bitchutecarousel-600x536.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"536\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-6781\" srcset=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/bitchutecarousel-600x536.png 600w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/bitchutecarousel-202x180.png 202w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/bitchutecarousel-768x686.png 768w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/bitchutecarousel-336x300.png 336w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/bitchutecarousel.png 813w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p class=\"lightboxtext\">click to enlarge the image</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"How to open YouTube lightbox in Elementor page builder\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:109:\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-video-lightbox/how-to-open-youtube-lightbox-in-elementor-page-builder/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 08 Nov 2018 23:26:38 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:3:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"WordPress Lightbox\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"WordPress Lightbox Plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:24:\"WordPress Video Lightbox\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:36:\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/?p=6752\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:432:\"Product: WonderPlugin Lightbox Tutorial: Elementor is a WordPress drag and drop page builder. This tutorial will show you how to open a YouTube video in a lightbox popup when clicking an Elementor button. In Elementor page builder, add a button. &#8230; <a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-video-lightbox/how-to-open-youtube-lightbox-in-elementor-page-builder/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;</span></a>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"WonderPlugin Support\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3189:\"<p><strong>Product</strong>:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-lightbox/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WonderPlugin Lightbox</a></p>\n<p><strong>Tutorial</strong>:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/elementor/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Elementor</a> is a WordPress drag and drop page builder. This tutorial will show you how to open a YouTube video in a lightbox popup when clicking an Elementor button.<br />\n<span id=\"more-6752\"></span></p>\n<p>In Elementor page builder, add a button. In the Edit Button panel, Content tab, enter the YouTube URL to the Link input box:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/elementor-youtube.png\" class=\"wplightbox\"><img src=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/elementor-youtube.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"298\" height=\"424\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-6753\" srcset=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/elementor-youtube.png 298w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/elementor-youtube-127x180.png 127w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/elementor-youtube-211x300.png 211w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 298px) 100vw, 298px\" /></a></p>\n<p>In the Advanced tab, in the input box Element Sytle -> CSS Classes, enter <code>wplightbox</code>:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/elementor-youtube-lightbox.png\" class=\"wplightbox\"><img src=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/elementor-youtube-lightbox.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"487\" height=\"698\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-6754\" srcset=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/elementor-youtube-lightbox.png 487w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/elementor-youtube-lightbox-126x180.png 126w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/elementor-youtube-lightbox-419x600.png 419w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/elementor-youtube-lightbox-209x300.png 209w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 487px) 100vw, 487px\" /></a></p>\n<p>You can add custom CSS class names to specify the lightbox maximum width and height, for example, adding <code>wplightbox-width-1024</code> and <code>wplightbox-height-576</code> will specify the lightbox maximum width and height as 1024 by 576.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/elementor-youtube-lightbox-size.png\" class=\"wplightbox\"><img src=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/elementor-youtube-lightbox-size.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"490\" height=\"695\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-6755\" srcset=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/elementor-youtube-lightbox-size.png 490w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/elementor-youtube-lightbox-size-127x180.png 127w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/elementor-youtube-lightbox-size-423x600.png 423w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/elementor-youtube-lightbox-size-212x300.png 212w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 490px) 100vw, 490px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Update and save the page then test the lightbox effect in the published webpage.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"How to add gallery shortcode to X theme Cornerstone page builder\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:120:\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-carousel-plugin/how-to-add-gallery-shortcode-to-x-theme-cornerstone-page-builder/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 08 Nov 2018 22:52:07 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26:\"WordPress Audio Player API\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"WordPress Carousel Plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:24:\"WordPress Gallery Plugin\";s:7: