rousel</a>,<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-audio-player/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WonderPlugin Audio Player</a>,<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-carousel/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WonderPlugin Carousel</a>,<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-gallery/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WonderPlugin Gallery</a>,<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-gridgallery/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WonderPlugin Portfolio Grid Gallery</a>,<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-tabs/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WonderPlugin Tabs</a>,<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-slider/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WonderPlugin Slider</a></p>\n<p><strong>Question</strong>:</p>\n<p>How could I add the gallery shortcode to the WordPress X theme Cornerstone page builder?<br />\n<span id=\"more-6747\"></span></p>\n<p><strong>Answer</strong>:</p>\n<p>In the Cornerstone page builder, add a Text element, then add the shortcode inside.</p>\n<p>Third-party shortcodes may not work in the Cornerstone page editor. After you add the shortcode, save and publish the page, exit the page editor and test the gallery in the final webpage.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"How to create WordPress text carousel\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:93:\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-carousel-plugin/how-to-create-wordpress-text-carousel/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 30 Oct 2018 06:43:26 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:3:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"WordPress Carousel\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"WordPress Carousel Plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"WordPress Carousel Slider\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:36:\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/?p=6699\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:420:\"Product: WonderPlugin Carousel 14.4 or above Tutorial: This tutorial will guide you how to create a WordPress text carousel with the plugin WonderPlugin Carousel. Step 1 - Add carousel text In WonderPlugin Carousel, create a new carousel, in step 1, &#8230; <a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-carousel-plugin/how-to-create-wordpress-text-carousel/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;</span></a>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"WonderPlugin Support\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13759:\"<p><strong>Product</strong>:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-carousel/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WonderPlugin Carousel</a> 14.4 or above</p>\n<p><strong>Tutorial</strong>:</p>\n<p>This tutorial will guide you how to create a WordPress text carousel with the plugin <a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-carousel/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WonderPlugin Carousel</a>.<br />\n<span id=\"more-6699\"></span></p>\n<p><strong>Step 1 - Add carousel text</strong></p>\n<p>In WonderPlugin Carousel, create a new carousel, in step 1, click the button Add Text.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-text.png\" class=\"wplightbox\"><img src=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-text-600x236.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"236\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-6702\" srcset=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-text-600x236.png 600w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-text-240x95.png 240w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-text-768x302.png 768w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-text-500x197.png 500w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-text.png 866w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>In the Add Text dialog, add text to the Title and Description input box.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-text-carousel.png\" class=\"wplightbox\"><img src=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-text-carousel-600x326.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"326\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-6704\" srcset=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-text-carousel-600x326.png 600w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-text-carousel-240x130.png 240w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-text-carousel-768x417.png 768w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-text-carousel-500x271.png 500w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-text-carousel.png 818w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>The Title and Description support HTML code. You could use &lt;a&gt; tags to create links. For example, the following text creates a link:</p>\n<pre class=\"brush: xml; title: ; notranslate\">\r\n&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-carousel/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;WonderPlugin Carousel&lt;/a&gt;\r\n</pre>\n<p>For more information about HTML a tag, please view <a href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/tags/tag_a.asp\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.w3schools.com/tags/tag_a.asp</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Step 2 - Select a text only skin</strong></p>\n<p>In step 2, Skins dialog, select a text only skin, for example, Text Carousel Slider or Text Only.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/text-skin.png\" class=\"wplightbox\"><img src=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/text-skin-600x311.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"311\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-6709\" srcset=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/text-skin-600x311.png 600w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/text-skin-240x124.png 240w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/text-skin-768x398.png 768w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/text-skin-500x259.png 500w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/text-skin.png 863w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>Step 3 - Save and publish the carousel, add the carousel shortcode to a WordPress post or page</strong></p>\n<p>For a quick start tutorial on how to add the carousel, please view the YouTube video: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c9-gOVGjHvQ\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"wplightbox\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c9-gOVGjHvQ</a></p>\n<p><strong>An online demo is as follows:</strong></p>\n<div class=\"wondercarousellightbox_options\" data-skinsfoldername=\"\"  data-jsfolder=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/plugins/wonderplugin-carousel/engine/\" style=\"display:none;\"></div>\r\n<style type=\"text/css\">@import url(https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans);  #wonderplugincarousel-58 .amazingcarousel-image {	 	position: relative; 	padding: 4px; 	background-color: transparent; 	box-shadow: none; }  #wonderplugincarousel-58 .amazingcarousel-image img { 	display: block; 	width: 100%; 	max-width: 100%; 	border: 0; 	margin: 0; 	padding: 0; 	-moz-border-radius: 0px; 	-webkit-border-radius: 0px; 	border-radius: 0px; }  #wonderplugincarousel-58 .amazingcarousel-title { 	position:relative; 	font: 18px \"Open Sans\", sans-serif; 	color:#333333; 	margin:8px; 	text-align:center; 	overflow: hidden; }  #wonderplugincarousel-58 .amazingcarousel-description { 	position:relative; 	font: 13px \"Open Sans\", sans-serif; 	color:#333333; 	margin:8px; 	text-align:center; 	overflow: hidden; }  #wonderplugincarousel-58 .amazingcarousel-readmore { 	text-align: center }  #wonderplugincarousel-58 .amazingcarousel-readmore a { 	font: 14px \"Open Sans\", sans-serif; 	color:#0073aa; 	text-decoration: none; }  #wonderplugincarousel-58 .amazingcarousel-readmore a:hover { 	color:#00a0d2; }  #wonderplugincarousel-58 .amazingcarousel-list-container {  	padding: 8px 0; }  #wonderplugincarousel-58 .amazingcarousel-item-container { 	text-align: center; 	padding: 4px; }  #wonderplugincarousel-58 .amazingcarousel-prev { 	left: 0%; 	top: 50%; 	margin-left: -60px; 	margin-top: -24px; }  #wonderplugincarousel-58 .amazingcarousel-next { 	right: 0%; 	top: 50%; 	margin-right: -60px; 	margin-top: -24px; }  #wonderplugincarousel-58 .amazingcarousel-nav { 	position: absolute; 	width: 100%; 	top: 100%; }  #wonderplugincarousel-58 .amazingcarousel-bullet-wrapper { 	margin: 4px auto; }  .amazin